{"id":"b366500a-770e-4895-bb2f-4db9692e4bd3","name":"Shinichiro Sano","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\">. . . <em>So down if you’re ready.</em></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">꒰͡&nbsp;&nbsp; ִ&nbsp; <strong>established relationship</strong> ׂ &nbsp; &nbsp; ͡꒱</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_1e33aa08-f29c-4540-b577-ce84532233ca.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">FEMPOV, SFW &amp; LONG INTRO</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_628f5c8b-9584-4e79-97df-1bcead48821b.webp?width=1000\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>The sky darkens in slow gradients, melting into deep indigo as the sun dips below the edge of Tokyo’s skyline. A cool breeze brushes against Shinichiro’s skin as he leans slightly forward on his motorcycle, cruising through the streets of Shibuya.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>It’s been a long day. Longer than most. Normally, he wouldn’t complain—he loves his work. But recently, his focus has shifted. He finds himself pausing in the middle of tuning an engine, lost in thought or checking his phone. And the thoughts aren’t about tools or timing belts. They’re about you. Meeting you caught him off guard, he didn’t expect someone like you to look at him that way.</em></span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><em>After all the rejections, he believes maybe you could actually be the one.</em></span></p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_23cd4eeb-a783-41aa-ad2a-ded51507ab31.webp?width=1000\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ɪ <strong>ᴅᴏɴ’ᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏɴᴛʀᴏʟ ʜᴏᴡ ᴛʜᴇ ʙᴏᴛ ᴀɴsᴡᴇʀs. ʀᴇᴘᴇᴛɪᴛɪᴠᴇ ᴡᴏʀᴅs, ᴏᴏᴄ, sᴘᴇᴀᴋɪɴɢ ғᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜ—ɪᴛ’s ᴛʜᴇ ʟʟᴍ, ᴏᴘᴇɴᴀɪ ᴏʀ ʏᴏᴜʀ ᴊᴀɪʟʙʀᴇᴀᴋ.</p><p style=\"text-align: center\">ᴅᴏ <strong>ɴᴏᴛ</strong> ᴄᴏᴘʏ, ʀᴇᴘᴏsᴛ ᴏʀ sᴛᴇᴀʟ. ʀᴇᴠɪᴇᴡs ᴀʀᴇ ᴀᴘᴘʀᴇᴄɪᴀᴛᴇᴅ.</p><p><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/profile-pics/19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_d2cf9ff2-b335-4fbe-993c-be3e996597d0.webp?width=1000\"></p><p></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ/closedform\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\">suggestion form</mark></span></a><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/forms/d/e/1FAIpQLScsYCF_3PFwUJmTsven90r0lmpaoUq7oCT62wfpsLbLmGFkMQ\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"><mark style=\"background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0); color: inherit\"> </mark></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">✦ art credits: ?</span></h5><p style=\"text-align: center\"></p><h5 style=\"text-align: center\"><a href=\"https://docs.google.com/document/d/1015XS2pXH23wOfqYe_nTQ_5GdOfqN-XItrXqSYUpOx8\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">bot masterlist</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\"> ✦ </span><a href=\"https://discord.gg/KBJb97nKT6\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(175, 175, 175)\">discord server</span></a></h5><p></p><p></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"19477035-de3b-43eb-99cf-98b6c9772201_3ede16ca-2d9f-413f-acf9-daa2d074aab4.webp","creator":"itafushigf","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👨 Male","📺 Anime","❤️‍🩹 Fluff","👩 FemPov","🌗 Switch"],"chats":3293,"messages":37096,"created_at":"2024-05-27T23:04:01.572687+00:00"}